@node "System" "System Requirements"

  Da Cool Patcher`s minimum requirements are:
  -------------------------------------------

  · an Amiga ;)
  · OS2.04 or higher
  · MUI needs to be installed on your system
  

  Recommended requirements:
  -------------------------

  · NewInstaller (util/wb/NewInstaller1_3.lha) for the installation
  · xfdmaster.library for decrunched patches (util/pack)
  · 68020+

@endnode

